        </div>
        <h1>App Under Construction</h1>
        <p>
            The full Brutalist Notes app is being rebuilt with modern web technologies.
            Check back soon for the complete note-taking experience.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="btn">Back to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
